.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/013-reorganize-script-lane-folders/spec.md:40:This phase moves the 16 deep-agent-improvement scripts plus the scorer subtree into agent-improvement, model-benchmark, and shared lane subdirs, making the two-lane split visible on disk for the last flat surface. It is the highest-risk phase because two path traps lie in wait: loop-host spawns children across all three lanes (TST-1 must stay byte-identical) and dispatch-model resolves config by walking up from `__dirname` (a wrong depth fails silently).
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/013-reorganize-script-lane-folders/spec.md:42:**Key Decisions**: three-lane classification (ADR-001), spawn-time lane resolution to preserve TST-1 (ADR-002), fix dispatch-model depth plus a positive config-load test (ADR-003), lib and tests stay at root (ADR-004)
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/013-reorganize-script-lane-folders/spec.md:71:This is **Phase 13** of the deep-agent-improvement model-benchmark mode decomposition. It is the last and highest-risk phase.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/013-reorganize-script-lane-folders/spec.md:73:**Scope Boundary**: Only the `scripts/` tree of the deep-agent-improvement skill: the 16 movable scripts plus the scorer subtree. `lib/`, `tests/`, `vitest.config.mjs`, `node_modules`, and `README.md` stay at the scripts root. References and assets were already lane-split in phase 010.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/013-reorganize-script-lane-folders/spec.md:128:| `.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md` | Modify | repoint every `scripts/<name>.cjs` literal to the lane path |
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/013-reorganize-script-lane-folders/spec.md:129:| `.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/README.md` | Modify | repoint script paths |
