.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/000-release-and-program-cleanup/005-stress-test/003-fix-mcp-runtime-stress-findings/001-search-intelligence-stress-playbook/002-search-scenario-execution/runs/I2/cli-codex-1/output.txt:8747:.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/010-graph-impact-and-affordance-uplift/008-deep-research-review/research/008-deep-research-review-pt-01/iterations/iteration-006.md:36:- D4 — HANDLED. `CacheArgsInput` accepts `causalEdgesGeneration`, and `buildCacheArgs` includes it only when `enableCausalBoost === true` and the value is finite (`.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/search-utils.ts:58`, `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/search-utils.ts:66`, `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/search-utils.ts:181`, `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/search-utils.ts:213`).
