    32	
    33	## 2. Hardening gate (Opus, Phase 005 close-out)
    34	
    35	A dedicated Opus 4.8 read-only hardening review covered the three areas the Phase 004 code review did not fully cover: docs-vs-code accuracy, the new D1-inter advisor probe, and non-regression. **Verdict: SHIP — 0 P0, 0 P1.**
