.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/gpt55/iterations/iteration-003.md:4001:.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/009-perfect-session-capturing/016-json-mode-hybrid-enrichment/001-initial-enrichment/scratch/agent-output-iter-002-A9.md:46:- [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/core/memory-metadata.ts:254-285, core/frontmatter-editor.ts:83-88]
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/gpt55/iterations/iteration-003.md:4007:.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/009-perfect-session-capturing/016-json-mode-hybrid-enrichment/001-initial-enrichment/scratch/agent-output-iter-001-A3.md:20:In `input-normalizer.ts`, when the AI provides explicit `triggerPhrases`, they are copied to `_manualTriggerPhrases` (line 451). These manual phrases are then passed to `buildSessionSummaryObservation()` as `facts` (line 278-279, line 550). However, the downstream template/frontmatter rendering likely adds auto-extracted phrases ON TOP of the manual ones, creating a diluted set where the intentional domain-specific phrases are buried among noise.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/gpt55/iterations/iteration-003.md:4010:.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/009-perfect-session-capturing/016-json-mode-hybrid-enrichment/001-initial-enrichment/scratch/agent-output-iter-001-A3.md:68:- What I would do differently: Start by finding the actual frontmatter rendering logic (likely in a template or renderer module) to complete the trigger phrase generation chain from JSON input to saved file.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/gpt55/iterations/iteration-003.md:4011:.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/009-perfect-session-capturing/016-json-mode-hybrid-enrichment/001-initial-enrichment/scratch/agent-output-iter-001-A3.md:71:Domain A (Pipeline Data Integrity): Trace the complete trigger phrase generation chain -- find the renderer/template that produces the final frontmatter trigger_phrases array, determine whether _manualTriggerPhrases survive or get overwritten by auto-extraction, and map the exact code path where the n-gram shingle extraction happens. This would close the gap between what input-normalizer stores and what ends up in the saved file.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/gpt55/iterations/iteration-003.md:4014:.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/scratch/codex-implement-014-runtime-prompt.md:152:- The test must FAIL if the fix from Lane A or Lane B is reverted — this is the whole point of the fixture floor.
