.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49515:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2548:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md:210:### US-001: Benchmark a model's best prompt framework (Priority: P0)
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49516:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2549:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md:212:**As a** skill maintainer, **I want** to run `/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop --mode=model-benchmark --executor=cli-opencode --model=minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`, **so that** I get a ranked prompt-framework result + winner without hand-porting a rig each time.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49517:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2550:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md:215:1. Given a model + variant set + fixtures, When I run the model-benchmark mode, Then it dispatches the model, scores outputs, hill-climbs, and writes a synthesis naming the winner.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49518:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2551:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md:230:- Should the model-benchmark mode also gain a "promotion" step (auto-apply the winning framework to the executor's prompt card), or stay synthesis-only (operator integrates manually, as 120/003 did)?
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49519:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2552:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md:231:- Should the ported eval-rig live inside deep-agent-improvement, or become a shared component under deep-loop-runtime that both the rig and the skill import? (Research leaned: keep it in the skill; revisit if a third consumer appears.)
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49520:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2553:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:3:description: "Phase 15 of 121: remediate the 014 two-lane deep-review findings - 1 confirmed P0 (Lane B command flag misparse), 16 P1 (security/traceability cluster), and 16 P2 advisories - with regression tests and explicit dispositions."
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49521:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2554:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:7:  - "Lane B command flag misparse fix"
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49522:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2555:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:12:    packet_pointer: "skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code"
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49523:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2556:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:38:The 014 two-lane deep review returned a CONDITIONAL verdict against the two-lane program (121/008-013). This packet remediates every active finding: 1 confirmed P0 (the Lane B command flags misparse to booleans because `loop-host.cjs` `parseArgs` does not accept space-form flags), a cluster of 16 P1 findings (security: write-capable grader dispatch, unquoted shell interpolation, fixture-id traversal, open-by-default criteria-exec, shared-tmp score cache; traceability: invalid outcomes, dropped executor fields, missing provenance, overwritten reports, non-packet-local pause state, a Lane A-referencing promotion gate, split config, stale agent-note paths), and 16 P2 advisories. Each finding gets exactly one disposition - FIXED with a test or adversarial check where applicable, or DOCUMENT-ACCEPT with rationale. The work preserves TST-1 byte-identity in `scripts/shared/loop-host.cjs` and keeps the vitest suite green.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49524:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2557:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:66:The 014 review audited the two-lane program shipped across 121/008-013. Lane A is agent-improvement (`/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop`). Lane B is model-benchmark (`/deep:start-model-benchmark-loop`, runtime loop-host `--mode=model-benchmark` then materialize plus run-benchmark, scorer pattern or 5dim, grader noop or mock or llm). Scripts are lane-separated under `scripts/{shared,agent-improvement,model-benchmark}/` plus `scripts/lib/`.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49525:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2558:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:68:**Scope Boundary**: Resolve every active 014 finding (1 P0 + 16 P1 + 16 P2) with exactly one disposition each - FIXED (real code or doc fix plus a test or adversarial check where applicable) or DOCUMENT-ACCEPT (an intended trusted-author boundary or by-design behavior, recorded with explicit rationale). No silent drops. Changes stay inside `.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/**`, the two Lane B workflow YAMLs and the `/deep:start-model-benchmark-loop` and `/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop` command docs, the agent mirror notes, and the advisor explicit-lane scorer.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49526:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2559:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:72:**Deliverables**: code and doc fixes plus regression tests for every FIXED finding; a per-finding disposition register in decision-record.md; green vitest and a verified Lane B command end-to-end run.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49527:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2560:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:84:The 014 deep review returned a CONDITIONAL verdict. One confirmed P0 makes the shipped `/deep:start-model-benchmark-loop` misbehave: `loop-host.cjs` `parseArgs` only accepts `--key=value` or bare flags, but all three Lane B command surfaces invoke loop-host with SPACE-form flags, so `profile`, `outputs-dir`, `scorer`, and `grader` all parse to `true`. Alongside the P0 sit 16 P1 findings (a security cluster around write-capable grader dispatch, unquoted shell interpolation, fixture-id path traversal, an open-by-default criteria-exec gate, and a shared-tmp score cache; plus a traceability cluster around invalid session outcomes, dropped LLM executor fields, missing scorer provenance on failure, overwritten reports, non-packet-local pause state, a Lane A-referencing Lane B promotion gate, split config paths, and stale agent-note script paths) and 16 P2 advisories.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49528:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2561:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:87:Ship every active 014 finding closed with exactly one disposition, the P0 verified end-to-end through the YAML command path, the security and traceability P1 cluster hardened with adversarial tests, and the documented-accept boundaries recorded with rationale, so Lane B is reliable and the two-lane program clears its CONDITIONAL verdict.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49529:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2562:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:96:- F-P0-1: teach `loop-host.cjs` `parseArgs` to accept `--key value` space-form (consume the next non-`--` token) while keeping `--key=value` byte-identical; add a space-form parser test
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/logs/synth.out:49530:-.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/gpt55/logs/iter-001.out:2563:.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/015-fix-deep-review-findings-for-two-lane-code/spec.md:98:- F-P1 traceability cluster: valid Lane B session outcome (F-P1-3), thread LLM executor and model fields (F-P1-4), benchmark plateau stop (F-P1-5), config-path consolidation (F-P1-6), scorer provenance on failure (F-P1-7), lane-resolution ordering (F-P1-8), candidate-keyed score cache (F-P1-12), per-iteration immutable reports (F-P1-13), packet-local pause state (F-P1-14), Lane B promotion gate (F-P1-15), agent-note script-path repoint across 4 mirrors (F-P1-16)
