    17	
    18	After Phase 001 (design research) completed, a dedicated implementation-deep-research phase was inserted at `002` (mirroring sibling packet 121, which ran design research **and** implementation research as separate phases before building its benchmark lane). The three downstream scaffold phases shifted up by one so the folder number matches execution order:
    19	
    20	| Was | Now |
