pt55/state-parts/iter-002.jsonl\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n11: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1780128900434,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f36550001iolyeF9PVe6Obb\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"e008bbad453d1a1918f619ab96595daf9d222dc3\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f354d3001DTrUVoFXD5y4M5\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":56792,\"input\":21143,\"output\":141,\"reasoning\":0,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":35508}},\"cost\":0.00864258}}\n12: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1780128902077,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f36bba001uBO2qOqOJAPhyK\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f36659001BU7ptanhUEFcTV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"snapshot\":\"3f81ddaf40d053159eb38a9196a7cda68975fb21\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n13: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128903012,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_7xllavgzls6o_1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/iterations/iteration-001.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/iterations/iteration-001.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Iteration 001 — RQ1 Scoring Dimensions + RQ7 Prior Art (MiniMax-2.7)\\n2: \\n3: ## Focus\\n4: RQ1: Define the scoring dimensions for benchmarking a skill's real-world utilization — routing/activation accuracy, unprompted reference/asset discovery, efficiency/bottlenecks, usefulness via skill-on/skill-off ablation, and structural connectivity (orphan refs, dead router keys). Plus RQ7: external prior art on tool/skill discoverability and routing evaluation (retrieval precision/recall, tool-selection accuracy, ablation, LLM-as-judge, agent-eval harnesses).\\n5: \\n6: ---\\n7: \\n8: ## Actions Taken\\n9: \\n10: 1. **Read deep-agent-improvement SKILL.md** — mapped the skill's two co-equal lanes (Agent-Improvement / Model-Benchmark), three pluggable seams (candidate-source, dispatcher, scorer), smart router (INTENT_SIGNALS, RESOURCE_MAP, RUNTIME_ASSETS), lane-aware references/assets organization, loop-host.cjs entry point with `--mode` flag, and the 5-dimension scoring rubric.\\n11: 2. **Read sk-doc SKILL.md and system-skill-advisor SKILL.md** — confirmed sk-doc validates doc shape/package-structure, and system-skill-advisor routes requests externally at ≥0.8 confidence. Lane C is positioned as distinct from both.\\n12: 3. **Reviewed sibling packet 121-deep... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128903501,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_7xllavgzls6o_2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/state-parts/iter-001.jsonl\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/state-parts/iter-001.jsonl</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"model\\\":\\\"minimax\\\",\\\"newInfoRati