 promotion.\\\\\\\"\\\\n4: allowed-tools: [Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep]\\\\n5: version: 1.9.0.0\\\\n6: triggers:\\\\n7:   - deep-agent-improvement\\\\n8:   - agent improvement loop\\\\n9:   - bounded agent improvement\\\\n10:   - 5-dimension scoring\\\\n11:   - integration scanner\\\\n12:   - dynamic profiling\\\\n13:   - model-benchmark mode\\\\n14:   - benchmark a model or prompt framework\\\\n15: ---\\\\n16: \\\\n17: <!-- Keywords: deep-agent-improvement, deep-agent-improvement, agent-improvement, benchmark-harness, score-candidate, promo... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n21: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1780128182598,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77e87144001KfveTZi3NqVLZn\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"4c4335ff3d497eebb8228610cdf572358cc4e8e2\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77e856030011zg8ndCRp9gJk1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":62442,\"input\":3914,\"output\":171,\"reasoning\":0,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":58357}},\"cost\":0.00488082}}\n22: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1780128190916,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77e891c3001ijUImHnLvd3j7E\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77e87260001PdYy7FlCn60EQi\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"snapshot\":\"ac9d9b603a3f03a804e5677c0b8fd1d53d8400c3\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n23: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128208423,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"call_function_uftsz8v8vckk_1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"mkdir -p \\\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/iterations\\\" && mkdir -p \\\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Publ