/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/iterations/iteration-001.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/iterations/iteration-001.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Iteration 001 — Measurement Framework + Prior Art Survey\\n2: \\n3: ## Focus\\n4: Establish RQ1 (scoring dimensions + weights + normalization) and RQ7 (prior art on tool/skill discoverability + routing efficiency measurement). Ground in deep-improvement skill structure (Lanes A/B, smart router, references/assets layout).\\n5: \\n6: ---\\n7: \\n8: ## Actions Taken\\n9: \\n10: 1. **Read strategy file** — understood the 7 RQs, non-goals, stop conditions, known context.\\n11: 2. **Read deep-agent-improvement SKILL.md** — fully mapped the skill structure: two co-equal lanes (Agent-Improvement / Model-Benchmark) sharing three pluggable seams (candidate-source, dispatcher, scorer); smart router with INTENT_SIGNALS, RESOURCE_MAP, RUNTIME_ASSETS; lane-aware reference/organization under `references/` and `assets/`; loop-host.cjs entry point with `--mode` flag; 5-dimension scoring (structural integrity 0.20, rule coherence 0.25, integration consistency 0.25, output quality 0.15, system fitness 0.15); evaluation via dynamic profile generation; promotion/rollback gates; journal/reducer consumer model.\\n12: 3. **Read sk-doc SKILL.md** (first 80 lines) + system-skill-advisor SKILL.md (first 80 lines) — confirmed sk-doc validates doc shape/package-structure, and system-skill-adviso... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n27: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128213992,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_ubgwhdmtc60x_2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/deltas/iter-001.jsonl\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/deltas/iter-001.jsonl</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"F1\\\",\\\"dimension\\\":\\\"structural\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"deep-improvement skill structure is self-referential on routing: INTINT_SIGNALS/RESOURCE_MAP/RUNTIME_ASSETS determine which sub-documents load\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\".opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md:97-214\\\"}\\n2: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"F2\\\",\\\"dimension\\\":\\\"architectural\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Three pluggable seams exist: candidate-source, dispatcher, scorer — Lane C can plug into the scorer seam for skill-benchmark mode\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\".opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md:275-280\\\"}\\n3: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"F3\\\",\\\"dimension\\\":\\\"structural\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Lane-aware reference organization under references/ and assets/ — skill-benchmark harness must observe which refs/assets load vs should have loaded\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\".opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md:81-88\\\"}\\n4: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"F4\\\",\\\"dimension\\\":\\\"distinction\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"sk-doc validates shape/package-structure, not behavioral usefulness — Lane C fills the behavioral gap\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\".opencode/skills/sk-doc/SKILL.md:14-20,.opencode/skills/sk-doc/SKILL.md:46-50\\\"}\\n5: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"F5... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n28: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1780128214258,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77e8ecf0001tDDxtfEQPEm5l4\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"4af033f546c8285008f7648b0bc659ce1455683e\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77e8d843001Mvwot1SsIN6pzy\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":95889,\"input\":227,\"output\":183,\"reasoning\":0,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":95479}},\"cost\":0.00601644}}\n29: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1780128217909,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77e8fb1a001T6KDlxWYZbLHu9\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77e8ede5001M3q7QdOTJHi5UI\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"snapshot\":\"1b0e6641fc77f97b6b9ea8eef997e4a4e5431344\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n30: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128251303,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_function_v7en1g3lksug_1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Iteration 001 — RQ1 Scoring Dimensions + RQ7 Prior Art (MiniMax-2.7)\\n\\n## Focus\\nRQ1: Define the scoring dimensions for benchmarking a skill's real-world utilization — routing/activation accuracy, unprompted reference/asset discovery, efficiency/bottlenecks, usefulness via skill-on/skill-off ablation, and structural connectivity (orphan refs, dead router keys). Plus RQ7: external prior art on tool/skill discoverability and routing evaluation (retrieval precision/recall, tool-selection accuracy, ablation, LLM-as-judge, agent-eval harnesses).\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Actions Taken\\n\\n1. **Read deep-agent-improvement SKILL.md** — mapped the skill's two co-equal lanes (Agent-Improvement / Model-Benchmark), three pluggable seams (candidate-source, dispatcher, scorer), smart router (INTENT_SIGNALS, RESOURCE_MAP, RUNTIME_ASSETS), lane-aware references/assets organization, loop-host.cjs entry point with `--mode` flag, and the 5-dimension scoring rubric.\\n2. **Read sk-doc SKILL.md and system-skill-advisor SKILL.md** — confirmed sk-doc validates doc shape/package-structure, and system-skill-advisor routes requests externally at ≥0.8 confidence. Lane C is positioned as distinct from both.\\n3. **Reviewed sibling packet 121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md** — the Lane B template established the mode selector pattern, pluggable seams, and the evaluator contract. Lane C inherits the same architecture.\\n4. **Synthesized RQ1 measurement framework** from deep grounding in the skill's own router design, the evaluator contract, and cross-referencing with prior art from Tau-Bench and Brown et al.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Findings\\n\\n### F-minimax-i1-1: The skill's smart router is self-referential — and this is the primary measurement target\\n\\nThe deep-imp... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n31: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1780128251600,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77e97ecc001WghApwYtYyGE5z\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"c1497b16491e419f8bfbb2444e005ef830d2a399\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77e8ede5001M3q7QdOTJHi5UI\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":102883,\"input\":3749,\"output\":3431,\"reasoning\":0,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":95703}},\"cost\":0.01098408}}\n32: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1780128253189,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77e98504001FNyy61Srr2ePap\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77e97fea001MQOxxkCH9t5tu4\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"snapshot\":\"3c88552a8d74969d5312be56bcd93c7eb4be1fb1\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n33: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128253832,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"