nd structural connectivity (orphan refs, dead router keys). Plus RQ7: external prior art on tool/skill discoverability and routing evaluation (retrieval precision/recall, tool-selection accuracy, ablation, LLM-as-judge, agent-eval harnesses).\\n5: \\n6: ---\\n7: \\n8: ## Actions Taken\\n9: \\n10: 1. **Read deep-agent-improvement SKILL.md** — mapped the skill's two co-equal lanes (Agent-Improvement / Model-Benchmark), three pluggable seams (candidate-source, dispatcher, scorer), smart router (INTENT_SIGNALS, RESOURCE_MAP, RUNTIME_ASSETS), lane-aware references/assets organization, loop-host.cjs entry point with `--mode` flag, and the 5-dimension scoring rubric.\\n11: 2. **Read sk-doc SKILL.md and system-skill-advisor SKILL.md** — confirmed sk-doc validates doc shape/package-structure, and system-skill-advisor routes requests externally at ≥0.8 confidence. Lane C is positioned as distinct from both.\\n12: 3. **Reviewed sibling packet 121-deep... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128903501,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_7xllavgzls6o_2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/state-parts/iter-001.jsonl\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/state-parts/iter-001.jsonl</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"model\\\":\\\"minimax\\\",\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.6,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"iter1\\\"}\\n\\n(End of file - total 1 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata