\\n\\nIntegrate your data with almost any app or tool in a few clicks.\\n\\n\\n\\n](https://www.browse.ai/integrations)[\\n\\nWebsites to APIs\\n\\nTurn any websites into an API in minutes.\\n\\n\\n\\n](https://www.browse.ai/website-to-api)[\\n\\nWeb scraping services\\n\\nFully managed web scraping and monitoring solutions.\\n\\n\\n\\n](https://www.browse.ai/managed-web-scraping)[\\n\\n250+ Prebuilt robots\\n\\nAutomatically extract data from top websites.\\n\\n\\n\\n](https://www.browse.ai/prebuilt-robots)\\n\\nPlatform Overview\\n\\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/687a4a92ac57a8731c4a3897/6932ee6791f3c620261e1ff6_RS-Mockup-1.png)\\n\\nExtract data from your first website for free\\n\\nScrape and monitor data on the best AI scraping platform. No coding required.\\n\\n[\\n\\nSign up\\n\\n](https://dashboard.browse.ai/signup)\\n\\nUse cases\\n\\nBy data category\\n\\n[\\n\\nPrice monitoring\\n\\nMonitor prices and products from any website reliably with no code.\\n\\n\\n\\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/price-monitoring)[\\n\\nE-Commerce\\n\\nReliably scrape and monitor product data, competitors, and vendors at scale.\\n\\n... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128182321,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_function_d9o8ac6jmgq3_2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research\",\"pattern\":\"skill.*benchmark|router.*test|routing.*accuracy|unprompted.*discovery|tool.*selection\"},\"output\":\"Found 80 matches\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/logs/iter-001.out:\\n  Line 4: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool_use\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1780128158678,\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\\\",\\\"part\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool\\\",\\\"tool\\\":\\\"read\\\",\\\"callID\\\":\\\"call_function_r6hfuyah5s92_1\\\",\\\"state\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"input\\\":{\\\"filePath\\\":\\\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md\\\"},\\\"output\\\":\\\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md</path>\\\\n<type>file</type>\\\\n<content>\\\\n1: ---\\\\n2: name: deep-agent-improvement\\\\n3: description: \\\\\\\"Evaluator-first bounded agent improvement: 5-dim scoring, dynamic profiling, packet-local candidates, guarded promotion.\\\\\\\"\\\\n4: allowed-tools: [Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep]\\\\n5: version: 1.9.0.0\\\\n6: triggers:\\\\n7:   - deep-agent-improvement\\\\n8:   - agent improvement loop\\\\n9:   - bounded agent improvement\\\\n10:   - 5-dimension scoring\\\\n11:   - integration scanner\\\\n12:   - dynamic profiling\\\\n13:   - model-benchmark mode\\\\n14:   - benchmark a model or prompt framework\\\\n15: ---\\\\n16: \\\\n17: <!-- Keywords: deep-agent-improvement, deep-agent-improvement, agent-improvement, benchmark-harness, score-candidate, promo... (line truncated to 2000 chars)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/logs/iter-001.out","time":{"start":1780128915872,"end":1780128915888}},"id":"prt_e77f3a197001PYIuVl5RiOZVaK","sessionID":"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND","messageID":"msg_e77f376b0001Agt6iv38MiDEgC"}}
