es_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f375bd001psTipaXHDo2b8o\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"98354d8c3cc7fdaf2b1fa9fc36fba4ed53bf3385\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f36659001BU7ptanhUEFcTV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":60463,\"input\":3471,\"output\":344,\"reasoning\":0,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":56648}},\"cost\":0.00485298}}\n18: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1780128910617,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f38d18001NJMT4DtP6ZJIEl\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f376b0001Agt6iv38MiDEgC\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"snapshot\":\"a50d253da6f707ea25ee35690f6786e77244a14e\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n19: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1780128915369,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f39fa2001netfP5IWx10PWS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f376b0001Agt6iv38MiDEgC\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nNow let me check the prior iteration files and the spec to understand the research trajectory:\\n\",\"time\":{\"start\":1780128915362,\"end\":1780128915364}}}\n20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128915631,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_fx7kciwu8yyz_1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: title: \\\"Phase 001: Skill-benchmark deep research (multi-model)\\\"\\n3: description: \\\"20-iteration multi-model deep research (5x MiniMax-2.7, 5x DeepSeek-v4-pro, 5x GPT-5.5-xhigh-fast, 5x Opus-4.8-native) investigating Lane C skill-benchmark design and the deep-agent-improvement->deep-improvement rename impact map.\\\"\\n4: trigger_phrases:\\n5:   - \\\"skill-benchmark deep research\\\"\\n6:   - \\\"122 phase 001\\\"\\n7:   - \\\"multi-model deep research skill benchmark\\\"\\n8: importance_tier: \\\"important\\\"\\n9: contextType: \\\"research\\\"\\n10: _memory:\\n11:   continuity:\\n12:     packet_pointer: \\\"skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research\\\"\\n13:     last_updated_at: \\\"2026-05-30T00:00:00Z\\\"\\n14:     last_updated_by: \\\"claude-opus\\\"\\n15:     recent_action: \\\"Authored research-phase spec; preparing multi-model deep-research runs\\\"\\n16:     next_safe_action: \\\"Run /deep:start-research-loop:auto per model (5 iters each) into research/\\\"\\n17:     blockers: []\\n18:     completion_pct: 5\\n19:     open_questions: []\\n20:     answered_questions: []\\n21: ---\\n22: <!-- SPECKIT_TEMPLATE_SOURCE: spec-core | v2.2 -->\\n23: <!-- SPECKIT_LEVEL: 2 -->\\n24: \\n25: # Phase 001 — Skill-benchmark deep research\\n26: \\n27: **Parent:** `122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode`\\n28: **Type... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n\n(End of file - total 20 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\u001b[93m\u001b[1m! \u001b[0m agent \"general\" is a subagent, not a primary agent. Falling back to default agent\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1780128890816,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f33fbc001zl9dElwdIUg3TV\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f32b4d001iXCdjrHgTVnzx2\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"snapshot\":\"bf929e93d345be736680fb39ed9c37e71ede4468\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1780128894479,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f34e0a001BSK4FrG45gn6K6\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f32b4d001iXCdjrHgTVnzx2\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nI'll research RQ3 (activation scoring: skill-advisor vs smart router) and RQ4 (fixture authoring avoiding circularity) for Lane C design. Let me gather ground-truth from the repo.\\n\",\"time\":{\"start\":1780128894474,\"end\":1780128894476}}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128894915,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_a31gbemw6wx3_1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: name: deep-agent-improvement\\n3: description: \\\"Evaluator-first bounded agent improvement: 5-dim scoring, dynamic profiling, packet-local candidates, guarded promotion.\\\"\\n4: allowed-tools: [Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep]\\n5: version: 1.9.0.0\\n6: triggers:\\n7:   - deep-agent-improvement\\n8:   - agent improvement loop\\n9:   - bounded agent improvement\\n10:   - 5-dimension scoring\\n11:   - integration scanner\\n12:   - dynamic profiling\\n13:   - model-benchmark mode\\n14:   - benchmark a model or prompt framework\\n15: ---\\n16: \\n17: <!-- Keywords: deep-agent-improvement, deep-agent-improvement, agent-improvement, benchmark-harness, score-candidate, promote-candidate, rollback-candidate -->\\n18: \\n19: # Recursive Agent: Evaluator-First Improvement Orchestrator\\n20: \\n21: Evaluator-first workflow for testing whether a bounded agent surface can be improved without immediately mutating the source of truth. It combines packet-local candidates, deterministic scoring, repeatable benchmarks, and explicit promotion or rollback gates.\\n22: \\n23: ---\\n24: \\n25: ## 1. WHEN TO USE\\n26: \\n27: ### Two Co-Equal Lanes\\n28: \\n29: This skill supports two co-equal use-case lanes that share the same candidate, dispatcher, and scorer seams:\\n30: \\n31: | Lane | Pick when | Command |\\n32: | --- | --- | --- |\\n33: | **Lane A: Agent-Improvement** | You want to improve a bounded agent `.md` file | `/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop` |\\n34: | **Lane B: Model-Benchmark** | You want to be... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128895316,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_a31gbemw6wx3_2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/SKILL.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/SKILL.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: name: system-skill-advisor\\n3: description: Routes non-trivial requests to matching skills through standalone MCP metadata and stable advisor tool ids.\\n4: allowed-tools: [Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep]\\n5: version: 0.1.0\\n6: trigger_phrases:\\n7:   - \\\"skill advisor\\\"\\n8:   - \\\"gate 2 routing\\\"\\n9:   - \\\"advisor_recommend\\\"\\n10:   - \\\"advisor_status\\\"\\n11:   - \\\"which skill should handle this\\\"\\n12:   - \\\"route this request to a skill\\\"\\n13:   - \\\"system skill advisor\\\"\\n14: keywords:\\n15:   - skill-routing\\n16:   - gate-2\\n17:   - advisor-mcp\\n18:   - legacy-tool-bridge\\n19:   - skill-graph\\n20:   - semantic-lane\\n21: intent_signals:\\n22:   - \\\"Gate 2 skill routing\\\"\\n23:   - \\\"advisor_recommend native MCP routing\\\"\\n24:   - \\\"advisor_status freshness check\\\"\\n25:   - \\\"which skill should handle this request\\\"\\n26:   - \\\"run the skill advisor hook\\\"\\n27: ---\\n28: \\n29: <!-- Keywords: system-skill-advisor, skill-advisor, advisor_recommend, advisor_status, advisor_rebuild, advisor_validate, skill_graph_scan, skill_graph_query, skill_graph_status, skill_graph_validate, skill_graph_propagate_enhances, cross-skill-edges, gate-2-routing, standalone-mcp, legacy-tool-bridge, skill-graph -->\\n30: \\n31: # System Skill Advisor\\n32: \\n33: <!-- sk-doc-template: skill_md -->\\n34: \\n35: Routes non-trivial user requests to the right skill through the standalone Skill Advisor MCP package.\\n36: \\n37: ---\\n38: \\n39: ## 1. WHEN TO USE\\n40: \\n41: Use this skill when the work is a... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128895654,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_a31gbemw6wx3_3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-doc/SKILL.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-doc/SKILL.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: ---\\n2: name: sk-doc\\n3: description: \\\"Markdown and OpenCode component specialist: doc quality, content optimization, component scaffolds, install guides, playbooks.\\\"\\n4: allowed-tools: [Bash, Edit, Glob, Grep, Read, Task, Write]\\n5: version: 1.5.0.0\\n6: ---\\n7: \\n8: <!-- Keywords: sk-doc, markdown-quality, skill-creation, document-validation, ascii-flowchart, llms-txt, content-optimization, extract-structure -->\\n9: \\n10: # Documentation Creation Specialist - Unified Markdown & Component Management\\n11: \\n12: Unified specialist providing: (1) Document quality pipeline with structure enforcement and content optimization, (2) OpenCode component creation (skills, agents, commands) with scaffolding, validation and packaging, (3) ASCII flowchart creation for visualizing workflows, (4) Install guide creation for setup documentation and (5) Feature catalog and manual testing playbook creation for inventory and validation packages.\\n13: \\n14: **Core Principle**: Structure first, then content, then quality.\\n15: \\n16: **Architecture**: Scripts handle deterministic parsing/metrics. AI handles quality judgment and recommendations.\\n17: \\n18: ## 1. WHEN TO USE\\n19: \\n20: ### Use Case: Document Quality Management\\n21: \\n22: Enforce markdown structure, optimize content for AI assistants, validate quality through script-assisted AI analysis.\\n23: \\n24: **README Creation** - Use `readme_template.md` + `readme_creation.md` when:\\n25: - Creating new README for any folder or project\\n26: - User requests \\\"create a RE... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1780128895963,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f353d8001Eo7m73rWVSWyt8\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f56995973698e7b9c82c7c113be6f3847a125a1d\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f32b4d001iXCdjrHgTVnzx2\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":36002,\"input\":33702,\"output\":491,\"reasoning\":0,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":1809}},\"cost\":0.01080834}}\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1780128898667,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77f35e68001SC1Ki633yhwacy\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77f354d3001DTrUVoFXD5y4M5\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"snapshot\":\"01384b354ac856d140800f88d594fd0b77c35cfe\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128899861,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1880cd6beffeAAFH1uk95wMSND\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_function_l06tnp5un5cu_1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchest