0.8 confidence. Lane C is positioned as distinct from both.\\n3. **Reviewed sibling packet 121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/spec.md** — the Lane B template established the mode selector pattern, pluggable seams, and the evaluator contract. Lane C inherits the same architecture.\\n4. **Synthesized RQ1 measurement framework** from deep grounding in the skill's own router design, the evaluator contract, and cross-referencing with prior art from Tau-Bench and Brown et al.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Findings\\n\\n### F-minimax-i1-1: The skill's smart router is self-referential — and this is the primary measurement target\\n\\nThe deep-imp... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n31: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1780128251600,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77e97ecc001WghApwYtYyGE5z\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"c1497b16491e419f8bfbb2444e005ef830d2a399\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77e8ede5001M3q7QdOTJHi5UI\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":102883,\"input\":3749,\"output\":3431,\"reasoning\":0,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":95703}},\"cost\":0.01098408}}\n32: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1780128253189,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e77e98504001FNyy61Srr2ePap\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e77e97fea001MQOxxkCH9t5tu4\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"snapshot\":\"3c88552a8d74969d5312be56bcd93c7eb4be1fb1\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n33: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128253832,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_function_kr6i3u4mmb73_1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"model\\\":\\\"minimax\\\",\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.6,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"iter1\\\"}\",\"filePath\":\"/Users/miche