roducts from any website reliably with no code.\\n\\n\\n\\n](https://www.browse.ai/use-cases/price-monitoring)[\\n\\nE-Commerce\\n\\nReliably scrape and monitor product data, competitors, and vendors at scale.\\n\\n... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1780128182321,\"sessionID\":\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_function_d9o8ac6jmgq3_2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research\",\"pattern\":\"skill.*benchmark|router.*test|routing.*accuracy|unprompted.*discovery|tool.*selection\"},\"output\":\"Found 80 matches\\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/minimax/logs/iter-001.out:\\n  Line 4: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool_use\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1780128158678,\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_18818249cffeInllmWUcVkPFl1\\\",\\\"part\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool\\\",\\\"tool\\\":\\\"read\\\",\\\"callID\\\":\\\"call_function_r6hfuyah5s92_1\\\",\\\"state\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"input\\\":{\\\"filePath\\\":\\\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md\\\"},\\\"output\\\":\\\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/SKILL.md</path>\\\\n<type>file</type>\\\\n<content>\\\\n1: ---\\\\n2: name: deep-agent-improvement\\\\n3: description: \\\\\\\"Evaluator-first bounded agent improvement: 5-dim scoring, dynamic profiling, packet-local candidates, guarded promotion.\\\\\\\"\\\\n4: allowed-tools: [Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep]\\\\n5: version: 1.9.0.0\\\\n6: triggers:\\\\n7:   -